rd accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide an href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","'react' is defined but never used.","eqeqeq","Expected '===' and instead saw '=='.","BinaryExpression","unexpected","'HomeSlider' is defined but never used.",[1182,1182]," rel=\"noreferrer\""]